Wearing Ink.com was once was a totally green digital tattoo magazine. It was designed to appeal to everyone searching for tattoos or tattoo designs. Our pages made it fun and easy to find tattoo ideas that were imaginative and meaningful. The features of this unique tattoo magazine were filled with words and images of people. They also showed tattoo places and tattoo designs to visually and verbally detail the amazing lives of those wearing tattoos
